ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period (from May 5, 2004 to May 4, 2005) during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. MICHEL DÉZIEL, a Puisne Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec, who was required to move from Sainte-Thérèse to Montréal.
